Subject: drm/amd/pm: Fix xgmi link control on aldebaran
Git-commit: 19e66d512e4182a0461530fa3159638e0f55d97e
Patch-mainline: v5.16-rc8
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

Fix the message argument.
	0: Allow power down
	1: Disallow power down

Signed-off-by: Lijo Lazar <lijo.lazar@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Hawking Zhang <Hawking.Zhang@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/pm/swsmu/smu13/aldebaran_ppt.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/pm/swsmu/smu13/aldebaran_ppt.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/pm/swsmu/smu13/aldebaran_ppt.c
index 59a7d276541d..7d50827cf0a8 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/pm/swsmu/smu13/aldebaran_ppt.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/pm/swsmu/smu13/aldebaran_ppt.c
@@ -1621,7 +1621,7 @@ static int aldebaran_allow_xgmi_power_down(struct smu_context *smu, bool en)
 {
 	return smu_cmn_send_smc_msg_with_param(smu,
 					       SMU_MSG_GmiPwrDnControl,
-					       en ? 1 : 0,
+					       en ? 0 : 1,
 					       NULL);
 }
 
